race.comment: THEYCALLMETHUNDER (4) is overdue for a win having finished runner-up at both runs this time in. Has the inside gate and with good early speed will take catching. JACK THE BOSS (1) returned from a long break over 1000m and although run off his legs early found the line strongly to finish fourth. Fitter for it and should feature late. WILF (5) made his debut at big odds but showed some ability, also getting back but running on hard. Improver worth following up.  UNA GENTLE (10) has been below best last coupe over 1200m when led and faded. Comes back in trip and will be in this for a long way at odds.
